description: Dark secrets are unearthed when a malign alien force from beyond the grave is unleashed aboard the ship General Lee and threatens to tear the War Pigs apart from within! As the search for Jim Raynor gathers pace, a team member's dark and blood-soaked past is laid bare, beginning a spiral of terror that pits War Pig against War Pig. Continue the journey into the extended galaxy of the best-selling video game!

The life of Alex's father is in deadly danger as he falls into the hands of a bloodthirsty vampire who has gone mad. Alex will do anything to save him, even joining forces with the deadly Red Hood, but will that be enough? It's a battle for power in Crimson #6!
name: The Children of Judas, Part Three: Running Mates

description: It's Christmas day. The first Christmas Alex has spent without his family. But that's the least of his worries, seven strange visitors have come to decide the future of Alex's existence. And an uninvited guest has come to wish Alex a "Merry Christmas" in a very particular way.
